Class TableBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.client.builder.TableBuilder

  • public class TableBuilder
extends Object
    Build a Table. The database name and table name must be provided, plus whatever is needed by the underlying StorageDescriptorBuilder.
